{"tid":1091286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夫婦生16個子女組超級大家庭　一餐食12個Pizza家務要分工","createTime":"2019-04-04T04:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T17:56:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fa24e4ccdbed75c67e65a571b6cbedf1712f1573","tid":1091286,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"現時很多夫婦只生一個小朋友，尤其是香港，3個以上孩子已經算多孩家庭。澳洲一對夫婦卻相繼生了16個子女組成一家18口，49歲的全職媽咪Jeni表示家庭成員多，必需列明家規，不論孩子是甚麼年紀，也要幫忙做家務，屋企才會打理得井井有條！<br />\n綜合外媒報道，現時澳洲最多產家庭是昆士蘭的Bonell家族，Bonell夫婦育有16位子女， 包括9名兒子及7位女兒，年齡由4歲至29歲不等，包括Jesse, Brooke, Claire, Natalie, Karl, Samuel, Cameron, Sabrina, Tim, Brandon, Eve, Nate, Rachel, Eric, Damian 和Katelyn。早年，一家18口住在同一屋簷下，現時有的子女另組織家庭或已搬出外生活，只剩下11位子女跟父母繼續一起生活。<br />\n要照顧16位孩子及做所有家務，憑媽媽Jeni一人之力很難。Jeni開設了facebook專頁及YouTube頻道「The Bonell Family」，分享了大家庭的生活。她表示，大家庭必須要保持秩序，故此訂立家規，有一份每周工作表，所有人都要分工安排負責有關工作，例如準備食物、墊枱擺餐具、洗碗、倒垃圾、執玩具、掃地、吸塵及清洗浴室等。<br />\n而工作時間表大約每3至6個月就會重新安排，全家人會商討如何分工，而不論任何年齡的孩子也要負責，小至12歲的孩子已經可以煮好一家人的晚餐，如果叫外賣，全家人要叫12個Pizza才夠吃。<br />\n而每人每天或每星期都有自己固定的工作，包括每朝收拾好床鋪才可吃早餐、摺衫、放好鞋子、不可亂放玩具要保持地板整潔、每星期打掃房間、每兩星期吸塵，以及每星期都要抹燈掣、茶几及門口等。<br />\nJeni表示，任何住在家中的人，就有責任做家務，而孩子長大後亦有離開家的一天，那時他們也要自己負責家務，所以從小學會分擔家庭責任很重要。現時，Bonell已有數位女兒、兒子已成家，生孩子另組自己的家庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2316495/family_thumb_20190403_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2316495%2Ffamily_thumb_20190403_J_1024.jpg&h=a9e3d264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2316495/p02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2316495%2Fp02_1024.jpg&h=90783f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2316495/p12_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2316495%2Fp12_1024.jpg&h=0d77de7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2316495/p07_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2316495%2Fp07_1024.jpg&h=8d578c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2316495/p11_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2316495%2Fp11_1024.jpg&h=b0bdb2b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2316495/p14_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2316495%2Fp14_1024.jpg&h=ad9201a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2316495/%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E7%94%9F16%E5%80%8B%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E7%B5%84%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E3%80%80%E4%B8%80%E9%A4%90%E9%A3%9F12%E5%80%8BPizza%E5%AE%B6%E5%8B%99%E8%A6%81%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2316495%2F%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E7%2594%259F16%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25A4%2590%25E9%25A3%259F12%25E5%2580%258BPizza%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvB4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=c72d7f0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2316495/%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E7%94%9F16%E5%80%8B%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E7%B5%84%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E3%80%80%E4%B8%80%E9%A4%90%E9%A3%9F12%E5%80%8BPizza%E5%AE%B6%E5%8B%99%E8%A6%81%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"ec0d44b2978b406ad6b3130ff2b57ffd0a1ad9c5","tid":1091286,"uid":161